  "repo_truth": "Review the exact remediated 53-path worktree subject against baseline fd6242fbab911eebb09a4d541a6e5e1e32dc5468. Review 2 returned CHANGES_REQUIRED for equality leakage of retained raw observation state, serializer admission of invalid typed records, retained public rich Project Context 0.1 exports, incomplete positive author/doctor proof, and one Clippy error. The parent split a public downstream-safe projection from an engine-private retained observation, removed equality-bearing raw state from public inspection types and flow, made serialization require and validate the selected decision/schema before emitting, removed both rich legacy export paths with compile-fail proof, added exact author and doctor/API projection proof, and cleared Clippy. Preserve the HCM-1.4 contract that the shipped conditional Environment Context remains indeterminate until a later condition-evaluator slice: the live Doctor Project Context row is positive/non-null with exact fingerprints while the shipped status/exit remains INDETERMINATE/nonzero; the exhaustive exit table separately proves READY exits zero.",
  "allowed_scope": [
    "Remain read-only and replay all 53 manifest hashes plus the aggregate before reviewing.",
    "Re-review every production and test byte, with priority on every review-1 and review-2 Required finding and their interactions.",
    "Run bounded read-only Rust, filesystem, API-surface, security, portability, and scope checks as needed.",
    "Return findings first with exact file/line evidence and the smallest in-scope remediation."
  ],
  "non_goals": [
    "No edits, staging, commits, handoff/ledger writes, or user task hops.",
    "No condition evaluator, definitions, schemas, Cargo, pipeline/stage, SDK/Tauri/Substrate/adapters, contract/dock, or HCM-2.2+ work.",
    "No legacy importer, dual read, persisted Markdown, general projection engine, setup materializer, or shipped-profile readiness reinterpretation."
  ],
  "tasks": [
    "Invoke the ordered required skills and return BLOCKED on any subject mismatch.",
    "Verify raw source bytes and descriptor identity live only in an engine-private observation and cannot be inferred through public equality, Debug, accessors, flow fields, logs, or errors.",
    "Verify the public selected serializer cannot emit any record outside the selected 1.0 schema and that private emitter framing plus public negative API proof are complete.",
    "Verify the retired rich Project Context 0.1 parser, Markdown validator, structured validator, module, and types are absent from the public engine surface, with compile-fail proof.",
    "Verify authoring reports exact byte length plus both fingerprints and Doctor/API/CLI exposes the exact stable non-null 1.1.0 row without violating the frozen shipped conditional INDETERMINATE status/exit contract.",
    "Recheck review-1 final stability, retired-path nonreads, multi-exclusion budget enforcement, mandatory edge proof, and all prior HCM-2.1 behavior.",
    "Return CLEAN only with no Critical or Required finding; otherwise CHANGES_REQUIRED or BLOCKED."
  ],
